name: "The Computer of 1984" - Galactibles™ #16
description: Holy Saint Jobs! You’ve discovered Galactible™ #16, the “Computer of 1984!” Collect this little thinking machine and take a trip back to 1984 to buy boat loads of Apple stock! This little compooter comes with some sick 80’s jams to keep you grooving as you traverse the Galactiverse. Your Mana has been raised by +400,000 bits! Comes with a custom beat and voice over by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
